attributes.description:
"It is undoubtedly a remarkable newcomer and further ascertains that for premium quality, you don’t always have to drive German cars." (Topgear review: May 27,2022)

Luxuriously detailed and designed, packed with the latest comfort, safety and convenience features, the Tiggo 8 Pro is a 7-seater, turbocharged, premium SUV.
With a lighting efficiency of around 2.7 times that of a traditional halogen lamp, the Tiggo 8 Pro’s lighting system radically improves road illumination and driving safety.
The N95-level air-conditioning purifier, filters more than 95% of particles and pathogens, while the AQS + PM2.5 air quality control system, automatically switches between inside and outside circulation to block harmful bacteria.
With third row seats down, the boot space is a massive 2101L, and even with these rear seats raised for the maximum seven-person occupancy, the boot space is still a very generous 1179L.
The Tiggo 8 Pro comes with seven colour themes for the interior ambient lighting, varying easily with the rhythm of your favourite music.
